# design-sync package-shape converter (staged scripts + build output)
.ds-sync/
ds-bundle/
# Symlink to the repo-root .design-sync/ (the durable config/previews/NOTES.md
# home) — package-build.mjs/package-capture.mjs resolve `.design-sync/*`
# relative to cwd, and cwd must be desktop/ for componentSrcMap's
# desktop-relative paths to resolve, so this symlink bridges the two.
# Recreate per clone: `ln -s ../.design-sync .design-sync` (run from desktop/).
.design-sync

